<p>In this study we analyzed the expression of the genes constituting the 70-gene breast cancer prognostic signature, as implemented in the MammaPrint assay, to develop novel and simple prognostic predictors based on the Top-Scoring-Pair (TSP) algorithm. 
Visit this <a href="https://bmcgenomics.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/1471-2164-14-336">page</a>
to read the original manuscript.</p>

